[A_Creature_t5_upregate H7Creature]
mName="Guardian of the depths".
mLore="With rare exceptions, the Depth Guards do not care about the problems of land dwellers, because all their efforts are aimed at holding back the unimaginable horrors that lurk in the darkest corners of the vast ocean. If at least one of those creatures managed to rise to the surface, then all common sea monsters that terrify sailors would seem like harmless kittens in comparison. To confront such formidable opponents, the Guards put on enchanted coral armor made by the best craftsmen of their people and fearlessly plunge into the abyss, where sunlight can not reach."

