[A_Creature_t5_base H7Creature]
mName="Guardian of the oceans"
mLore="For centuries, legends about an unknown Merfolk race, whose representatives come to the aid of ships in trouble, repel attacks of pirates and monsters, and then return back to the sea, have been passed in the taverns from one sailor to another. Although such stories are generally considered nothing more than mere tales, there is written evidence that in the past one of the Sea Elf crews managed to develop close ties with the so-called Ocean Guards. The latest rumor is that Guards have been seen in the ranks of Shanria troops, however, due to the philosophy of the children of Shalassa, who prefer not to contact the outside world unless absolutely necessary, it is not possible to shed light on the origins of their mysterious allies."

